<section class="hero">
  <a href="#" class="pill">
    <span class="pill-badge">NEW</span>
    <span>Programme d'accélération IA pour PME — Q3 2026</span>
    <span class="pill-arrow">→</span>
  </a>
  <h1>
    L'infrastructure cloud,<br />
    conçue par un <span class="grad-text">ingénieur</span>.
  </h1>
  <p class="lede">
    Architecture Azure, migrations Microsoft 365 et intégration IA pour les PME
    et grandes organisations. Pas de discours commercial — juste de l'ingénierie
    qui tient en production.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Planifier un appel découverte →</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn-ghost">Voir les références</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 5;
    padding: 110px 48px 120px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 5px 6px 5px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .pill:hover {
    border-color: var(--line-strong);
  }
  .pill-badge {
    background: var(--grad);
    padding: 3px 11px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bg);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .pill-arrow {
    color: var(--fg-faint);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(44px, 7vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    max-width: 1080px;
  }
  .hero h1 :global(.grad-text) {
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    animation: gradMove 10s ease infinite;
  }
  .hero p.lede {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    max-width: 660px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    padding: 15px 28px;
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      transform 0.15s,
      box-shadow 0.2s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px var(--cyan-glow);
  }
  .btn-ghost {
    padding: 15px 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    color: var(--fg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s,
      background 0.2s;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    background: rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 70px 24px 80px;
    }
  }
</style>
